release_note: This version includes large font support custom date range selection during PDF and CSV export HEX code usage when selecting theme colors and bug fixes.
This version includes new color customization options the capability to write for future dates and notification badges!
This release includes automatic device syncing and supports an upgraded remote database. There are also a couple of minor bug fixes.

Version 2.0 has many new highly requested features! Customize the color theme Change the daily questions Track your mood and learn about yourself with the mood dashboard Lock your app with Face ID Touch ID with your device password or with your Morning! account password Export your journal to PDF or CSV
Highly requested feature: you can now edit past entries! Midnight is no longer the deadline to practice your daily gratitude. Enjoy!
You can now view update your daily answers from different devices by signing in with your account. We ve also adapted this app for the iPad so you can practice gratitude from your favorite device!
You can now authenticate! Sign up and join the community to be the first to have access to new upcoming features!
